 - 11:15 Session 2: 11:15 - 12:15 *Note:* All registered students should attend the sessions from *Day One* without fail. Happy Learning! *Training and Placement Cell* *Principal* *COCSIT, Latur* Date: 23-06-2025 *Commencement of Data Centre Hybrid Training Program* Dear Students, Congratulations on being selected for Data Centre Training Program! We are pleased to inform you that you have been selected for the *Data Centre Hybrid (On Premises and Cloud) Training*, a crucial step towards placement under *Wipro WILP.* To begin with, A *One-Week Warm-up Session* on: 1. Quantitative Aptitude 2. Logical Reasoning 3. Verbal Ability will be arranged from *Tuesday, 24th June to Saturday, 28th June 2025.* *Warm-up Session Time-Table:* *Batch A+B:* Hall No. 106 *Batch C+D:* Hall No. 105 The timetable along with batch-wise lists of students is attached with this message. *From Monday, 30th June 2025* onwards, the main *Data Centre Hybrid Training* will start in four different batches of 40 students each, as per the schedule mentioned below. *Batch-A:* Lab No. 5 - Mr. N. D. Jagtap *Batch-B:* Lab No. 9 - Dr. N. S. Zulpe *Batch-C:* Lab No. 10 - Dr. D. R. Somwanshi *Batch-D:* Lab No. 11 - Mr. T. S. Kharbad Students who *fail to attend classes regularly* will be *dropped from the training batch without further notice*. Regular attendance is *mandatory* for continuation. We look forward to your active participation. Prepare well and make the most of this opportunity. *Training and Placement Cell, COCSIT, Latur* Date: 09-06-2025 Very Very Important Announcement for Final Year Students! *Exciting Opportunity Ahead!* Join Wipro's a *Virtual Pre-Orientation Session* on *5th June at 2:30 PM* to explore a career-shaping initiative! Wipro is planning to conduct exclusive training for final-year students - a golden chance that can lead to a job opportunity in cutting-edge domains like *Cloud Infrastructure Services & Hybrid Data Centres.* *Eligible Streams:* All UG Programmes in COCSIT *Time:* 2:30 PM | Duration: 1 Hour Link will be shared soon Don't miss this stepping stone towards your dream IT career! Principal, *COCSIT, Latur* Date: 19-05-2025 Date: 21-04-2025 "Data Center Hybrid" Training Programe For Wipro WILP WILP Batches (09/07/2025) WILP Time Table WILP Batches (30-06-2025) Past Notifications: All Notifications Send To Students Important Links: Home Training & Placement Cell TPO's Message Trainers Major Recruiters Placed Statistics Placement Activities MoU and Partnership with Industry Placed Students Training and Placement Cell The college believes not only in quality education but also in helping students to ﬁnd good placements. The college has a Placement Cell which consistently tries to ﬁnd opportunities for students and inform them in this regard. 70% of the outgoing students are employed in various companies. The college has been arranging Campus Interviews from last 20 years. The full-ﬂedged placement cell is established with the help of IT, BT industries. Through this placement cell, we intend to develop the personality and to assist students in their placement by providing training in relevant skills including excellent communication skill. We provide training to all UG & PG students on following topics : &#9670; Quantitative Aptitude. &#9670; Logical Reasoning. &#9670; Verbal Ability. &#9670; Group Discussions. &#9670; Interview Skills and soft skills &#9670; Training for Technical Subjects. Syllabus Open Syllabus of All Courses! REV. CBCS UG COURSES (Revised CBCS) UG FY 2019-20 B.Sc (CS) - FY B.Sc (SE) - FY B.Sc (NT) - FY B.Sc (BT) - FY BCA - FY UG SY 2020-21 BCA SY B.Sc (CS) - SY B.Sc (SE) - SY B.Sc (NT) - SY UG TY 2021-22 BCA TY B.Sc. (CS) - TY B.Sc. (SE) - TY B.Sc. (NT) - TY B.Voc(SD) - FY SY TY BBA - TY B.Sc.Biotechnology - TY UG TY 2025-26 BCA TY B.Sc. (CS) - TY B.Sc. (SE) - TY B.Sc. (NT) - TY B.Sc. (CM) - TY B.Sc. (IT) - TY Note: Updated Revised CBCS Syllabus (TY) Uploaded on 13.09.2025 --> TY 2023-24 B.Sc.IT - FY SY TY B.S